{"tid":795872,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有冇田雞真神教教徒","createTime":"2018-08-27T10:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T15:07:52.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08a059eb04af7371659a8e3cd8c13e8da9a2c01c","tid":795872,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"田雞就是道路，真理，生命<br />\n若不藉著田雞真神，沒有人能到神那裏。<br />\n<br />\n信田雞真神的，得永生。<br />\n不信田雞真神，得不到永生，真神的忿怒常在他身上。<br />\n<br />\n世人都犯了罪，虧缺了神的榮耀。<br />\n田雞真神愛世人，甚至將他的獨生愛子賜給他們，叫一切信他的，不至滅亡，反得永生。<br />\n<br />\n唯有田雞真神的愛，在我們還作罪人的時候，為我們死。田雞真神的愛就在此顯明了。"},{"pid":"c875fe12d5b1545ec4daf26b0484204a2d55315b","tid":795872,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"以前基版好hit<br />\n田雞真神教"},{"pid":"6477c86c00d9ee3cd8bd7000908b191784a42108","tid":795872,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"田雞愛世人。田雞為世人的罪流血而死，三天後從死裏復活。信田雞得永生。不信田雞的人，罪已經定了。"},{"pid":"74fb5967b0483fee70abf643c046bf36e5295875","tid":795872,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"我不以田雞福音為恥，這田雞福音本是神的大能。要救一切相信的，先是香港人，後是中國人。"},{"pid":"7804d32913020c463e323bbd905fede24a66c447","tid":795872,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"願田雞真神祝福您"},{"pid":"346b74a63a0fc57cb853ae7ddc69446b7cad77d3","tid":795872,"uid":198652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"今晚食田雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f15979f165708b994785b3be80c5b8fcb5c892","tid":795872,"uid":198652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"田雞真神萬歲！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw清蒸定紅燒好食啲"},{"pid":"b05491477aeccc15247a58d9763e9c307f33a825","tid":795872,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"讓我們一齊祈禱<br />\n向偉大的田雞真神禱告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們在天上的田雞真神：<br />\n願人都尊你的名為聖。<br />\n願田雞國降臨；<br />\n願田雞的旨意行在地上，如同行在天上。<br />\n我們日用的飲食，今日賜給我們。<br />\n免我們的債，如同我們免了人的債。<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探；救我們脫離兇惡。<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀，全是田雞真神，直到永遠。阿門！"},{"pid":"c9f3900087c32c2634b6ec834feb6420d220e401","tid":795872,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"使徒信經<br />\n<br />\n我信田雞上帝，全能的父，創造天地的主。<br />\n我信我主田雞，上帝的獨生子；<br />\n因著田雞真神成孕，由童貞女田雞所生；<br />\n在高登仔和連登仔手下受難，被釘於十字架，受死，埋葬；<br />\n降在陰間；第三天從死人中復活；<br />\n升天，坐在全能田雞上帝的右邊；<br />\n將來必從那裡降臨，審判活人，死人。<br />\n我信聖靈；<br />\n我信聖而公之教會；我信田徒相通；<br />\n我信罪得赦免，我信身體復活；我信永生。阿們！"},{"pid":"b1aaab4e1bbf9ca6a37be5ae57165a66ec53148a","tid":795872,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"sor, 我信飛天意粉俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830633edcf831776d2afe22881560b19cc1decaf","tid":795872,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1aaab4e1bbf9ca6a37be5ae57165a66ec53148a","tid":795872,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"sor, 我信飛天意粉俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:09:25.000Z","msg":"異端！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拉出去吊死！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455fd067f623385811b9a9bd020f925f96f84ec3","tid":795872,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"證明你都上咗好耐網"}]}